TRAFFICKING -- BOLIVIA; UNITED STATES -- MILITARY AID -- BOLIVIA; UNITED STATES 
-- MILITARY AID -- PERU; UNITED STATES -- MILITARY AID -- COLOMBIA; UNITED 
STATES -- POLITICS; CONGRESS (U.S.); BUSH, GEORGE 
</P>
