POSSESSIONS; LITHUANIA -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- USSR; LITHUANIA -- TRADE -- 
USSR; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- LITHUANIA; SECESSION; NATIONALISM; 
EMBARGOES; BLOCKADES; LITHUANIA -- LABOR; LAYOFFS; BARTER; LITHUANIA -- 
GOVERNMENT 
</P>
