She counsels new arrivals. JOAN M. ZOPF-PAHOYO / Los Angeles Times; Photo, 
Cathy Anacker draws on personal experience in her job as head of alcohol and 
drug dependency panel. TERESA TAMURA / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Marcellus 
Robinson, left, directs Via Avanta in Pacoima. 
</P>
