reportage of Hawkey's performance LARRY KAPLAN / For The Times; Photo, THE REV. 
FLOYD ROSE: pastor of Family Baptist Church, who participated in sit-in at 
Toledo City Hall LARRY KAPLAN / For The Times 
</P>
