through sixth grade. No cost. Call 933-4226. 
</P>
<P>
SIMI VALLEY 
</P>
<P>
Rancho Simi Recreation and Park District; two day camps at Rancho Simi Park and 
Sequoia Park, running June 25 through Aug. 31. Operates 9 a.m. to 4 p.m. plus 
extended care. Offers swimming, arts and crafts, sports, fishing, field trips. 
Cost, $65. Call 584-4400. 
</P>
<P>
Girl Scouts; one week of day camp, July 16-20, at Santa Susana Park for 
kindergarten through sixth grade. Camp runs 2 p.m. to 7:30 p.m., focus on 
old-time country days, crafts, sports and games. Cost, $28. Call 564-4848. 
</P>
<P>
THOUSAND OAKS 
</P>
