camps for ages 6 to 14. Cost, $60 a week. Also sports camps for basketball and 
soccer. Cost, $50-$59. Recreational day camp Aug. 13-17 for disabled children, 
ages 6 to 13 from 10 a.m. to 2 p.m. Call 495-6471. 
</P>
<P>
