City of Ventura Recreation Department; day camp June 18 through Aug. 24. 
One-week or two-week sessions specializing in such things as soccer, nature, 
gymnastics, tennis, arts, volleyball, beach sports and travel. Age range varies 
from 6 to 14, depending on activity. Cost varies, but about $80 a week. Call 
658-4726. 
</P>
