YMCA; from June 18 through Aug. 31, two day camp programs for first through 
fifth grade, and sixth through eighth grade. Runs 9 a.m. to 4 p.m. with 
extended care. Offers swimming, games, crafts and outing. Cost, $80 a week. 
Also offers one-week overnight camps. Call 642-2131. 
</P>
