</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Health Checkup: Dr. Susan M. Swank, an orthopedic surgeon at Downey Community 
Hospital, was incorrectly identified in a photo caption published Sunday. Swank 
was shown checking students from the Downey Unified School District for 
scoliosis, which is curvature of the spine. 
</P>
