<TEXT>
<P>
Candidate Funds: A story published Sunday on fund raising in the 42nd 
Congressional District race failed to mention that Bryan Stevens, former 
president of the California Teachers Assn., is also competing for the 
Democratic nomination. Stevens says he plans to spend $500 on his primary 
campaign. 
