<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Elsmere Canyon -- An article Wednesday about Los Angeles City Council action on 
a proposed Elsmere Canyon garbage dump incorrectly reported the votes of two 
council members. Councilman Nate Holden voted for the proposal; Councilman Joel 
Wachs voted against it. 
</P>
